; Regression test for issue #1164: aliases won't work in cli (BZ#1164)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1164
; Tests that account alias directives in the journal file are properly
; expanded when ledger is invoked from the command line.

alias Chk = Assets:Checking
alias Savings = Assets:Savings

2024/01/01 Paycheck
    Chk         $1000.00
    Savings      $500.00
    Income:Salary

test bal
            $1500.00  Assets
            $1000.00    Checking
             $500.00    Savings
           $-1500.00  Income:Salary
--------------------
                   0
end test
